	<h1 class="title">银行制度改革，中国政府希望引入更多风险</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/img/missing_face.png" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name"> Neil Gough</span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2015-05-04 08:01:00 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/9105/medium/9105.jpg?1436688429" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


